            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">The specimen submitted is of an Australian Acacia, but as neither flowers nor fruits are on the branches, it will not be safe to name the species. What looks like a fruit is a gall. Such galls are use...</supplied>
